I've just downloaded this version.
It has a small National Geographic Tag on the top left hand side and the resolution is 688 x 432.

By the way, I personally like the voice of Sean Pertwee much better than Alec Baldwin's.
Can someone please seed it? if they do and it's good quality i'll keep it seeding at 2 meg/sec for several months before taking it down.
